eqAtmOamPmTable.name: eqAtmOamPmTable
eqAtmOamPmTable.description: This table contains OAM Performance Monitoring stats for an ATM OAM PM Session.

eqAtmOamPmEntry.name: eqAtmOamPmEntry
eqAtmOamPmEntry.description: An ATM logical port stats entry.

eqAtmOamPmIfIndex.name: eqAtmOamPmIfIndex
eqAtmOamPmIfIndex.description: The ifIndex for the corresponding atm logical port.

eqAtmOamPmStatus.name: eqAtmOamPmStatus
eqAtmOamPmStatus.description: Indicates whether the activation process is in the middle of activating, has successfully connected, has failed to connect because the remote end did not respond, or couldn't setup the connection because of lack of local resources.

eqAtmOamPmSessionType.name: eqAtmOamPmSessionType
eqAtmOamPmSessionType.description: Identifies the PM session to perform Continuity Check or Performance Monitoring.

eqAtmOamPmSinkSource.name: eqAtmOamPmSinkSource
eqAtmOamPmSinkSource.description: Identifies the PM session to be sink, source, or both.

eqAtmOamPmBlockSize.name: eqAtmOamPmBlockSize
eqAtmOamPmBlockSize.description: The Block Size of User cells transmitted before an OAM PM cell is transmitted.

eqAtmOamPmEndPt.name: eqAtmOamPmEndPt
eqAtmOamPmEndPt.description: Identifies the PM Session as either a Segment Endpoint or an End-to-End Point

eqAtmOamPmFlow.name: eqAtmOamPmFlow
eqAtmOamPmFlow.description: Identifies the Flow as either an F4 (Virtual Path) or F5 (Virtual Channel) flow.

eqAtmOamPmDirection.name: eqAtmOamPmDirection
eqAtmOamPmDirection.description: Identifies the direction as either Forward (Egress, toward the outside netword) or Backward (Ingress, toward the switch fabric)

eqAtmOamPmTimeout.name: eqAtmOamPmTimeout
eqAtmOamPmTimeout.description: Identifies the Time Period in which to timeout an Activation/DeActivation Cell (in which case another cell may be sent depending on the Retry Count).

eqAtmOamPmRetryCount.name: eqAtmOamPmRetryCount
eqAtmOamPmRetryCount.description: Number of times to retry Activation in the event of a failure (no response).

eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp0.name: eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp0
eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp0.description: The number of Clp0 cells transmitted.

eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp01.name: eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp01
eqAtmOamPmFwdTxUserCellsClp01.description: The number of Clp0 plus Clp1 cells transmitted.
